      • getAvroFile

        public DataFileReader<GenericRecord> getAvroFile(String file)
                                          throws FileBasedHelperException
        Returns an DataFileReader to the specified avro file.

        Note: It is the caller's responsibility to close the returned DataFileReader.

        Parameters:
        file - The path to the avro file to open.
        Returns:
        A DataFileReader for the specified avro file.
        Throws:
        FileBasedHelperException - if there is a problem opening the InputStream for the specified file.
